    {cmd:invnt(}{it:df}{cmd:,}{it:np}{cmd:,}{it:p}{cmd:)}
{p2colset 8 22 22 2}{...}
{p2col: 描述:}逆累积非中心学生t分布：
	if {cmd:nt(}{it:df}{cmd:,}{it:np}{cmd:,}{it:t}{cmd:)} = {it:p}，则
	{cmd:invnt(}{it:df}{cmd:,}{it:np}{cmd:,}{it:p}{cmd:)} = {it:t}{p_end}
{p2col: 域 {it:df}:}1 到 1e+6（可以是非整数值）{p_end}
{p2col: 域 {it:np}:}-1,000 到 1,000{p_end}
{p2col: 域 {it:p}:}0 到 1{p_end}
{p2col: 范围:}-8e+307 到 8e+307{p_end}
{p2colreset}{...}